{"word":"G2569 - καλοποιέω - kalopoiéō - kal-op-oy-eh'-o - Well doing","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">καλοποιέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">kalopoiéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kal-op-oy-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Well doing</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நன்மைசெய்"},{"paragraph":"to do well, act uprightly"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2570 - καλός - kalós - kal-os'/2570\">G2570</a> and <a href=\"#/G4160 - ποιέω - poiéō - poy-eh'-o/4160\">G4160</a>; to <i>do well</i>, that is, live virtuously: - well doing.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}